Hi everyone, my name is Greco. I am from Chile, which is in South America.

I am speaking for women in my country.

Now, the situation is still challenging for many women In Comoros, Colombia, and everywhere, we must fighting for women human rights, and be continue.

I hope everyone cares about it and helps any women around the world in need.

Please do not lose my words. This is an extraordinary responsibility which takes me to far distances, never been walking before.

Good Luck, Comoros, other countries, and all the world.
